Offered at $542,000

Welcome to this darling home in the heart of Belgrade! As you approach, a lovely front covered porch greets you, setting the tone for the warmth and charm that awaits inside. Step through the front door into a spacious living room, beautifully designed with vaulted ceilings and a cozy gas fireplace. The living room seamlessly flows into the kitchen and dining area, making it an ideal space for entertaining. The kitchen is well-appointed with modern appliances and ample counter space, while the dining area offers direct access to your incredible backyard and deck. Outdoor living at its finest awaits you in this expansive, fully fenced, and landscaped yard. Enjoy the hot tub, gather around the fire pit, or simply unwind on the large deck, perfect for summer barbecues and evening relaxation. This bright and inviting home features two comfortable bedrooms and a full bathroom on one end, offering privacy and convenience for family or guests. On the other end, discover your serene primary en-suite, complete with a spacious walk-in closet. The home is finished off with a nice laundry room that leads to your 2-car attached garage.
